title: Anilas My First Colouring Book Set of 4 Colouring Books, Ideal for Toddlers, Nursery & Preschool Children (Ages 3-6)
features: Children's Colouring books with fun colourful borders. This set of 4 books are 4 different themed books, all with vibrantly coloured covers to help engage the child.
Inside the book, each page includes an interesting and clear design to colour, as well as a fun colourful border around the edge of the page for added fun.
Each book contains 16 pages (32 sides) with 17 pictures to colour in with examples on the left page and the dimensions are 210x210mm.
Useful sized colouring books are perfect for traveling and fun at home,
Ideal for children aged 3-6 for keeping them entertained for hours.
